metadata.name: End of the Run
metadata.description:
18x24" Pencil & Markers 98lb - 160gsm Multimedia Paper

Herein lies the end of the run. At the edge of this peak: the end of our fun. It's time to move on, the next stage is near. No more moons in these skies, a degenerate's worst fear.  Here marks the end of this run. Off we go to find more fun. 

Created May - July 2022
